msgctxt "680"
msgid "Businessman"
msgstr "Empresario"

msgctxt "684"
msgid "Tanimura"
msgstr "Tanimura"

msgctxt "84_Businessman"
msgid "At the end of this street there's a young girl collecting donations."
msgstr "Al final de esta calle hay una jovencita recogiendo donaciones."

msgctxt "96_Businessman"
msgid "But only homeless people hang around there. Can't imagine she's collecting too much..."
msgstr "Pero solo hay sintechos por ahí. No creo que haya conseguido mucho..."

msgctxt "108_Tanimura"
msgid "(Collecting donations in a homeless area? That just might lead to a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default>. I should go and check it out.)"
msgstr "(¿Recogiendo donaciones donde hay sintechos? Puede que esto sea una <Color:7>revelación<Color:Default>. Debería ir a revisar)."

